Upgrading Support Incident Tracker
----------------------------------

To upgrade simply copy all the new files over the existing ones being careful not to overwrite
your config.inc.php or any custom themes you might have.  Then run setup.php in your browser.

Further instructions and notes about specific upgrades follow:


Upgrading from 3.20 to 3.21
---------------------------

Email templates can now insert updates into the incident log that are hidden from the customer view.
You should review your email templates and set the update visibility of each.

The config variable attachment_path has been renamed to attachment_fspath and a new variable
attachment_webpath has been created for the web view of the same path